ROLES:
builder: build(barrack); build(terranSupplyDepot).
mineralGatherer: gather(minerals);returned(Minerals).

OBJECTIVES: 
build(barrack).
build(terranSupplyDepot).
gather(minerals).

OBLIGATIONS:
mineralGatherer: returned(Minerals) < bel(me(Me)) | gathering(Minerals).
builder: build(terranSupplyDepot) < false | supply(X,Y), Res is Y-X, 6 > Res .
builder: build(barrack) <  false | org(alreadyBuilt(terranSupplyDepot,N)), N > 0, 3 > N.

RULES:
org(alreadyBuilt(Type,N)) :- findall(_, friendly(_, Type, _, _, _, _, _), L), length(L, N).
